data.name: Panel1.ToolTip
data.value:
WinMonitorAA is a software that allows you to reset the screen resolution to the settings you set.
In Windows many times when you change the monitor, it is a headache, if your current monitor has less resolution than the previous one, you must change the resolution manually without seeing. with the screen completely dark.
WinMonitorAA Solves this problem, just by pressing the key combination:
-------------------> ( Ctrl + Alt + A )
